The paper discusses the development of a recommender system framework for mobile app development, which involves the use of ontology and semantic web technology as well as machine learning techniques. This suggests that the paper could fall under the sub-categories of software engineering (cs.SE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), social and information networks (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Among these, software engineering and artificial intelligence seem to be the most relevant sub-categories, followed by information retrieval and social and information networks, and finally machine learning.
